file_content.text: You just signed your own death warrant.
I'm coming for you, understand? You're dead.
This isn't over.
How high do I have to stack the corpses before you get the message?
You will not continue to murder Jedi with impunity.
There will be no more even-handed offers. Only swift, definitive retribution.
I'm an enemy you're gonna regret making.
You made a big mistake, Jedi.
We've only just begun.
I'll find you. I always do.
My thoughts exactly.
You'll try.
Shut up.
I'm done with you. [Hang up.]
Party all ruined, boss's friends all dead.... What boss want to do now?
Party time's over. There's nothing left for us here.
We move on.
Blizz not in mood for party anymore anyway.
We find out who that Jedi is, and we make him very sorry.
Avenge the other hunters.
Boss and Blizz beat up stupid Jedi real good!
Nobody tries to kill me. Nobody.
Show the Jedi who's boss.
So... we make stupid Jedi sorry? Boss?
I'd rather not be here when security comes to see who's been shooting up their place.
No argument here.
We're done here.
First time for everything.
After you, I insist.
They can deal. I want a minute to pay my respects.
These hunters deserve better.
Hey, you want to foot the bill for this mess, be my guest.
I'm in no mood for questions.
It'd be their funeral.
Then let's just beat feet and make it easier on everybody.
What about them?
They get buried. We've got bigger problems.
Nothing we can do for them.
Nu kyr'adyc, shi taab'echaaj'la.
We pay our respects, with a hole in that Jedi's head.
We avenge them.
Skira. I can get behind that.
What about them?
You ask like I care.
Thought they were comrades. My mistake.
Did--did we just get them killed?
Thinking about it won't bring them back.
What's done is done.
No, but--Braden and Jory, Anuli, now them....
What if it were me?
That Jedi dragged them into this, not us.
This wasn't our fault.
It's not just them, it's everybody. Braden, Jory, Anuli, Soongh...
What if I'm next?
Are you finished?
You done whining?
Yeah, I'm finished.
Being has-beens got them killed.
They couldn't hack it.
They came here to throw you a party, not war with the Republic. Now they're dead. Because of us.
Are you going to be this callous when you get me killed?
Nobody lays a finger on you while I'm still breathing.
You won't die with me around.
I... I'm sorry. I was just starting to get over things, now this. Let's just go.
Shut your mouth before I do.
Can it!
O--okay.
Everyone who gets near you dies. I'm sick of it!
We're going to make enemies, Mako.
What do you want me to say?
I know, but you go out of your way to--and we aren't the ones who pay for it.
Then walk. I don't care.
Maybe you're right.
Is everyone who gets near us going to end up dead?
This isn't the place for a breakdown.
Pull it together.
I know... let's just get out of here.
I wont let this happen again.
Not if I can help it.
We can't be everywhere at once.
Better get used to it.
You might accept that. I won't.
Torian, round everyone up. We're leaving.
On it. Trouble?
Loads. I'll explain later.
Yeah.
Understood.
Just Jedi trying to put me away again.
Had some party crashers.
I'll keep an eye out.
Somebody just made the top of my hit list.
I plan on making some.
Sounds bad. We'll be ready.
Mako, get everyone back to the ship. We're leaving.
Huh? But I just finished getting ready.
Just do it. I'll explain later.
No arguments.
I'll get everything ready.
We had party crashers, Mako. It's a bloodbath.
This is serious.
You're kidding... you're not kidding. Okay, I'm on it.
You already missed the fun, unless you like mopping up blood.
Party's over anyway.
What? Tell me you didn't... oh, just explain it when you get here.
